USAGreenland — Backend (Canonical Store)
=======================================

PURPOSE
-------
SQLite Canonical Store + seeds + migrations.
Backend does NOT render pages directly.

IMPORTANT
---------
• Do NOT open .html files directly from disk
• Front-end rendering requires running the local server
• Backend DB changes do NOT auto-update the site yet

COMMON COMMANDS
---------------

Go to project root:
cd "$env:USERPROFILE\OneDrive\Desktop\USA GREENLAN SITE FILES"

Start front-end server:
npx http-server . -p 5500

Go to backend/store:
cd "$env:USERPROFILE\OneDrive\Desktop\USA GREENLAN SITE FILES\backend\store"


SQLite (explicit path):
C:\sqlite\sqlite3.exe usagreenland.db

LOCATION
--------
DB file: backend\store\usagreenland.db
Seeds:   backend\store\seeds_*.sql
